rn','U','{3}{G}','4','2','2',NULL,'All creatures able to block Prized Unicorn do so.','#_"The desire for its magic horn inspires such bloodthirsty greed that all who see the unicorn will kill to possess it."£—Dionus, elvish archdruid_#',NULL,'Sam Wood','287','5','£10/1/2009: Prized Unicorn doesn’t give a creature the ability to block it. It just forces those creatures that are already able to block it to do so. For example, it can’t force a creature that’s tapped or affected by a spell or ability that says it can’t block to block it. If there’s a cost associated with having a creature block, its controller isn’t forced to pay that cost, so the creature doesn’t have to block Prized Unicorn in that case either.£10/1/2009: If a creature the defending player controls can’t block Prized Unicorn, it can block any attacking creature, or not block at all.£10/1/2009: If two Prized Unicorns are attacking, each creature the defending player controls can block either one of them. (The defending player chooses.) A creature that can block multiple creatures, like Palace Guard, must block both of them.','G',NULL,'0.07','0.3','0.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'G','珍奇独角兽','珍奇獨角獸','Licorne prisée','Preziöses Einhorn','Unicorno Stimato','尊き一角獣','Unicórnio Cobiçado','Ценный Единорог','Unicornio preciado','희귀한 유니콘','生物～独角兽','生物～獨角獸','Créature : licorne','Kreatur — Einhorn','Creatura — Unicorno','クリーチャー ― ユニコーン','Criatura — Unicórnio','Существо — Единорог','Criatura — Unicornio','생물 — 유니콘','所有能够阻挡珍奇独角兽的生物皆须阻挡之。','所有能夠阻擋珍奇獨角獸的生物皆須阻擋之。','Toutes les créatures capables de bloquer la Licorne prisée le font.','Alle Kreaturen, die das Preziöse Einhorn blocken können, tun dies.','Tutte le creature in grado di bloccare l''Unicorno Stimato lo fanno.','尊き一角獣をブロックできるすべてのクリーチャーは、これをブロックする。','Todas as criaturas aptas a bloquear Unicórnio Cobiçado o fazem.','Все существа, способные блокировать Ценного Единорога, блокируют его.','Todas las criaturas que puedan bloquear al Unicornio preciado lo hacen.','희귀한 유니콘을 방어할 수 있는 모든 생물은 희귀한 유니콘을 방어해야 한다.','#_「其神奇犄角引发的占有欲能导致浓烈的嗜血贪欲，让所有见到这独角兽的人都要杀掉它好独占犄角。」～妖精高位德鲁伊戴欧诺_#','#_「其神奇犄角引發的佔有慾能導致濃烈的嗜血貪欲，讓所有見到這獨角獸的人都要殺掉牠好獨占犄角。」～妖精高位德魯伊戴歐諾_#','#_« Le désir de posséder sa corne magique inspire une telle envie meurtrière que quiconque voit la licorne va tuer pour la posséder. »—Dionus, archidruide elfe_#','#_„Das Verlangen nach seinem magischen Horn wird oft zu einer so blutrünstigen Gier, dass alle, die das Einhorn sehen, es deswegen zu töten versuchen."—Dionus, elfischer Erzdruide_#','#_"Il desiderio per il suo corno magico ispira una tale cupidigia assetata di sangue che tutti quelli che vedono l''unicorno uccideranno per averlo."—Dionus, arcidruido elfico_#','#_「その魔法の角に対する欲望は、かくも血なまぐさい強欲さを呼び起こし、ついにはその一角獣を見た者は、それを手に入れるために殺そうとするに至る。」――エルフの大ドルイド、ダイオヌス_#','#_"O desejo por seu chifre mágico inspira uma avidez tão violenta que todos que o veem matariam para tê-lo."— Dionus, arquidruida élfico_#','#_«Стремление обладать его волшебным рогом вселяет такую кровожадную алчность, что все, кто видят единорога, готовы убивать, лишь бы заполучить его».— Дионус, эльфийский архидруид_#','#_"El deseo por su cuerno mágico inspira una avaricia tan sangrienta que todos los que ven al unicornio matarán para poseerlo". —Dionus, archidruida élfico_#','#_"유니콘의 마법 뿔은 귀한 물건이라 유니콘을 본 사람은 그것을 죽이고 뿔을 차지하려는 핏빛 욕망에 휩싸인다."—엘프 대드루이드 디오너스_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('398479','Psychic Rebuttal','ORI','Instant','U','{1}{U}','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Counter target instant or sorcery spell that targets you.£Spell mastery — If there are two or more instant and/or sorcery cards in your graveyard, you may copy the spell countered this way. You may choose new targets for the copy.','#_"I know what you''re thinking," Jace whispered in the mage''s mind. "It''s not going to work."_#',NULL,'Todd Lockwood','67','5','£6/22/2015: The target instant or sorcery spell can have other targets as long as one of them is you.£6/22/2015: If the spell mastery ability applies, you’ll create a copy of the instant or sorcery spell only if Psychic Rebuttal counters that spell. If that spell can’t be countered by spells or abilities, you won’t get a copy.£6/22/2015: If Psychic Rebuttal creates a copy of the spell, you control the copy. That copy is created on the stack, so it’s not “cast.” Abilities that trigger when a player casts a spell won’t trigger. The copy will then resolve like a normal spell, after players get a chance to cast spells and activate abilities.£6/22/2015: The copy will have the same targets as the spell it’s copying unless you choose new ones. You may change any number of the targets, including all of them or none of them. If, for one of the targets, you can’t choose a new legal target, then it remains unchanged (even if the current target is illegal).£6/22/2015: If the copied spell is modal (that is, it says “Choose one –” or the like), the copy will have the same mode. You can’t choose a different one.£6/22/2015: If the copied spell has an X whose value was determined as it was cast, the copy has the same value of X.£6/22/2015: You can’t choose to pay any additional costs for the copy. However, effects based on any additional costs that were paid for the original spell are copied as though those same costs were paid for the copy too. For example, if a player sacrifices a 3/3 creature to cast Fling, and you copy it, the copy of Fling will also deal 3 damage to its target.£6/22/2015: If the copy says that it affects “you,” it affects the controller of the copy, not the controller of the original spell. Similarly, if the copy says that it affects an “opponent,” it affects an opponent of the copy’s controller, not an opponent of the original spell’s controller.£6/22/2015: Check to see if there are two or more instant and/or sorcery cards in your graveyard as the spell resolves to determine whether the spell mastery ability applies. The spell itself won’t count because it’s still on the stack as you make this check.','U',NULL,'0.04','0.24','1.2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'U','心灵抗辩','心靈抗辯','Réfutation psychique','Psychische Zurückweisung','Rifiuto Psichico','精神的反論','Repulsão Psíquica','Психический Отпор','Refutación psíquica','정신 반격','瞬间','瞬間','Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント','Mágica Instantânea','Мгновенное заклинание','Instantáneo','순간마법','反击目标瞬间或法术咒语，且该咒语须以你为目标。精熟咒语～如果你坟墓场中有两张或更多的瞬间和／或法术牌，则你可以复制以此法被反击的咒语。你可以为该复制品选择新的目标。','反擊目標瞬間或巫術咒語，且該咒語須以你為目標。精熟咒語～如果你墳墓場中有兩張或更多的瞬間和／或巫術牌，則你可以複製以此法被反擊的咒語。你可以為該複製品選擇新的目標。','Contrecarrez le sort d''éphémère ou de rituel ciblé qui vous cible.Maîtrise de sort — S''il y a au moins deux cartes d''éphémère et/ou de rituel dans votre cimetière, vous pouvez copier le sort contrecarré de cette manière. Vous pouvez choisir de nouvelles cibles pour cette copie.','Neutralisiere einen Spontanzauber oder eine Hexerei deiner Wahl, der bzw. die dich als Ziel hat.Zauberkunst — Falls sich zwei oder mehr Spontanzauber- und/oder Hexerei-Karten in deinem Friedhof befinden, kannst du den auf diese Weise neutralisierten Zauberspruch kopieren. Du kannst neue Ziele für die Kopie bestimmen.','Neutralizza una magia istantaneo o stregoneria bersaglio che ti bersaglia.Arte magica — Se nel tuo cimitero ci sono due o più carte istantaneo e/o stregoneria, puoi copiare la magia neutralizzata in questo modo. Puoi scegliere nuovi bersagli per la copia.','あなたを対象とするインスタント・呪文１つかソーサリー・呪文１つを対象とし、それを打ち消す。魔巧 ― あなたの墓地にインスタント・カードやソーサリー・カードが合わせて２枚以上あるなら、あなたはこれにより打ち消された呪文をコピーしてもよい。あなたはそのコピーの新しい対象を選んでもよい。','Anule a mágica instantânea ou o feitiço alvo que tenha você como alvo.Maestria em magia — Se houver dois ou mais cards de mágica instantânea ou feitiço no seu cemitério, você poderá copiar a mágica anulada desta forma. Você pode escolher novos alvos para a cópia.','Отмените целевое мгновенное заклинание или заклинание волшебства, целью которого являетесь вы.Мастерство заклинаний — Если на вашем кладбище есть не менее двух карт мгновенных заклинаний и #_(или)_# волшебства, вы можете скопировать отмененное таким образом заклинание. Вы можете выбрать новые цели для этой копии.','Contrarresta el hechizo objetivo de instantáneo o de conjuro que te hace objetivo.Dominio de hechizos — Si hay dos o más cartas de instantáneo y/o de conjuro en tu cementerio, puedes copiar el hechizo contrarrestado de esta manera. Puedes elegir nuevos objetivos para la copia.','당신을 목표로 정한 순간마법 또는 집중마법 주문을 목표로 정한다. 그 주문을 무효화한다.주문 숙련 — 당신의 무덤에 집중마법 그리고/또는 순간마법 카드가 두 장 이상 있다면, 당신은 이런 식으로 무효화된 주문을 복사할 수 있다. 당신은 그 복사본의 목표를 새로 정할 수 있다.','#_「我知道你在想什么，」杰斯的声音在法师的心灵中飘荡。「没用。」_#','#_「我知道你在想什麼，」傑斯的聲音在法師的心靈中飄蕩。「沒用。」_#','#_« Je sais ce que tu penses, murmura Jace dans l''esprit du mage. Mais ça ne marchera pas. »_#','#_„Ich weiß, was du denkst", ertönte Jaces Stimme im Geist des Magiers. „Es wird nicht funktionieren."_#','#_"So cosa stai pensando", sussurrò Jace nella mente del mago. "Non funzionerà."_#','#_ジェイスは魔道士の頭の中に囁いた。「お前が何を考えているかなんて、すべてお見通しだ。それが成功することなど、万に一つもあり得ない。」_#','#_"Eu sei o que você está pensando", sussurrou Jace na mente do mago. "Não vai funcionar."_#','#_«Я знаю, что ты задумал, — прошептал голос Джейса в разуме волшебника. — Ничего не выйдет»._#','#_"Sé lo que estás pensando", susurró Jace a la mente del mago. "No va a resultar"._#','#_"난 네 계획을 알고 있지." 제이스가 그 마도사의 마음에 속삭였다. "실패할 거야."_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('398427','Pyromancer''s Goggles','ORI','Legendary Artifact','M','{5}','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{T}: Add {R}. When that mana is spent to cast a red instant or sorcery spell, copy that spell and you may choose new targets for the copy.','#_"I hope to meet Jaya Ballard someday. I think we''d get along."—Chandra Nalaar_#',NULL,'James Paick','236','5','£6/22/2015: The mana produced by Pyromancer’s Goggles can be spent on anything, not just a red instant or sorcery spell.£6/22/2015: Any red instant or sorcery spell you spend the mana on will be copied, not just one that requires targets.£6/22/2015: The delayed triggered abili